### Create a workout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test-user",
  "startTime": "2026-01-27T10:00:00",
  "notes": "Push day"
}

### Get weekly volume
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/analytics/weekly-volume?weekStart=2026-01-27

### Get AI Coaching Recommendation (auto-fetch recent workouts)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/coach/recommend?numWorkouts=5&userGoals=strength&fitnessLevel=intermediate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get AI Coaching Recommendation (manual workout data)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/coach/recommend
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "recentWorkouts": [
    {
      "date": "2026-05-15",
      "exercises": [
        {
          "name": "Bench Press",
          "category": "chest",
          "totalSets": 4,
          "averageReps": 8,
          "averageWeight": 225,
          "averageRPE": 8
        },
        {
          "name": "Incline Dumbbell Press",
          "category": "chest",
          "totalSets": 3,
          "averageReps": 10,
          "averageWeight": 60,
          "averageRPE": 7
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "userGoals": "build muscle and increase strength",
  "fitnessLevel": "intermediate"
}
